A bitcoin [[currency_exchange]]/trading platform site headquartered in the USA in the State of Michigan.

##History

The exchange launched first with an open public bet on July 8, 2012 (2.1) after two months of preparation on testnet (2.2).

BitMe, LLC is a limited liability company registered in the State of Michigan, in the U.S.

